
sample_tmc: Generate random bytes

To run (load and start) container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 run sample_tmc.img

Enter the size of random data to be generated to a file:
$ printf 10 > testfile
$ cmtest data -f100 testfile

The number of generated random bytes is the same as the
number written to the testfile:
write data...0x064:2...read data...0x064:10...
00000000: 28 55 e0 2e c8 f5 8f f6  87 b7                    |(U........|
OK

To unload container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 unload
